We love how easy it is to save and search for recipes, and themed collections like Easy Cakes, Beer Cocktails, and A Taste of New Orleans are a mouthwatering delight. The app also features dozens of short instructional videos on topics like trussing chicken and julienning peppersperfect for novice chefs eager to dive in and start cooking.
